      <title>Version 1.6</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>PastScreen 1.6 - Multi-screen & clipboard polish</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>ScreenCaptureKit fixes:</strong> Captures respect the active display, eliminating shifted regions and invalid parameter errors.</li>
          <li><strong>Overlay reliability:</strong> The Liquid Glass selector converts coordinates correctly across monitors and cleans up instantly after cancel.</li>
          <li><strong>Clipboard smarts:</strong> Browsers/design tools now get both image data and a fallback file path, while IDEs like Zed still receive path-only content.</li>
          <li><strong>Outlook detection:</strong> Microsoft Outlook is treated as a browser so captures paste the full PNG by default.</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
